title: The Big Bang Theory Season 7 Episode 2
description:
A woman who moves into an apartment across the hall from two brilliant but socially awkward physicists shows them how little they know about life outside of the laboratory.



The Hofstadter Insufficiency
Sheldon and Penny bond over missing Leonard. Howard tries to help Raj get over his breakup with Lucy. Amy and Bernadette are away together at a biology convention.
